  <para style="p">
    <verse number="26" style="v" />Ὡσαύτως δὲ καὶ τὸ πνεῦμα συναντιλαμβάνεται τῇ ἀσθενείᾳ ἡμῶν· τὸ γὰρ τί προσευξώμεθα καθὸ δεῖ οὐκ οἴδαμεν, ἀλλ᾽ αὐτὸ τὸ πνεῦμα ὑπερεντυγχάνει<note caller="8" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">8.26 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">{A} </char><char style="fk" closed="false">ὑπερεντυγχάνει </char><char style="ft" closed="false">ℵ* A B D F G 6 81 256 263 424<char style="add">c</char> 1319 1506 1573 1739 1881 2127 it<char style="add">b, d*, g</char> arm (Origen) Epiphanius<char style="add">1/4</char>; Augustine<char style="add">14/17</char> Ps-Vigilius<char style="add">1/3</char> ⫽ </char><char style="fk" closed="false">ὑπερεντυγχάνει ὑπὲρ ἡμῶν </char><char style="ft" closed="false">ℵ<char style="add">2</char> C Ψ 33 104 424* 436 459 1175 1241 1852 1912 1962 2464 <char style="it">Byz</char> [K L P] <char style="it">Lect</char> it<char style="add">ar, d<char style="add">2</char>, f, mon, o</char> vg syr<char style="add">h</char> cop<char style="add">sa, bo</char> eth geo slav Origen<char style="add">lat</char> Eusebius (Diodore) Didymus<char style="add">lat</char> Didymus<char style="add">dub</char> (Macarius/Symeon) (Severian) Epiphanius<char style="add">3/4</char> Chrysostom (Theodore) (Cyril) (John-Damascus); Novatian Hilary Ambrosiaster Gregory-Elvira Ambrose Jerome Pelagius Maximinus Augustine<char style="add">3/17</char> Ps-Vigilius<char style="add">1/3</char> REB BJ TOB BTI DHH ⫽ </char><char style="fk" closed="false">ὑπὲρ ἡμῶν ἐντυγχάνει </char><char style="ft" closed="false">2200</char></note> στεναγμοῖς ἀλαλήτοις· <verse number="27" style="v" /><note caller="*" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">8.27 </char><char style="xq" closed="false">ὁ δὲ … καρδίας </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="PSA 139:1">Ps 139.1</ref>; <ref loc="1CO 4:5">1 Cor 4.5</ref></char></note>ὁ δὲ ἐραυνῶν τὰς καρδίας οἶδεν τί τὸ φρόνημα τοῦ πνεύματος, ὅτι κατὰ θεὸν ἐντυγχάνει ὑπὲρ ἁγίων. <verse number="28" style="v" /><note caller="*" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">8.28 </char><char style="xq" closed="false">τοῖς ἀγαπῶσιν … ἀγαθόν </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="EPH 1:11">Eph 1.11</ref>; <ref loc="EPH 3:11">3.11</ref></char></note>οἴδαμεν δὲ ὅτι τοῖς ἀγαπῶσιν τὸν θεὸν πάντα συνεργεῖ<note caller="9" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">8.28 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">{B} </char><char style="fk" closed="false">συνεργεῖ </char><char style="ft" closed="false">ℵ C D F G Ψ 6 33 104 256 263 424 436 459 1175 1241 1319 1506 1573 1739 1852 1881 1912 1962 2127 2200 2464 <char style="it">Byz</char> [K L P] <char style="it">Lect</char> it<char style="add">ar, b, d, f, g, mon, o</char> vg syr<char style="add">p, h</char> cop<char style="add">bo</char> arm geo slav Clement Origen<char style="add">gr, lat</char> Eusebius Cyril-Jerusalem Diodore (Gregory-Nyssa) Didymus Macarius/Symeon Chrysostom Cyril Hesychius Theodoret; Lucifer Ambrosiaster Ambrose Jerome Pelagius Augustine ⫽ </char><char style="fk" closed="false">συνεργεῖ ὁ θεός </char><char style="ft" closed="false">𝔓<char style="add">46</char> A B 81 cop<char style="add">sa</char> eth GNB EU BJ DHH</char></note> εἰς ἀγαθόν, τοῖς κατὰ πρόθεσιν κλητοῖς οὖσιν. <verse number="29" style="v" /><note caller="*" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">8.29 </char><char style="xq" closed="false">πρωτότοκον … ἀδελφοῖς </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="COL 1:18">Col 1.18</ref>; <ref loc="HEB 1:6">He 1.6</ref></char></note>ὅτι οὓς προέγνω, καὶ προώρισεν συμμόρφους τῆς εἰκόνος τοῦ υἱοῦ αὐτοῦ, εἰς τὸ εἶναι αὐτὸν πρωτότοκον ἐν πολλοῖς ἀδελφοῖς· <verse number="30" style="v" />οὓς δὲ προώρισεν, τούτους καὶ ἐκάλεσεν· καὶ οὓς ἐκάλεσεν, τούτους καὶ ἐδικαίωσεν· οὓς δὲ ἐδικαίωσεν, τούτους καὶ ἐδόξασεν.</para>
  <para style="s">God’s Love</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="31" style="v" />
    <note caller="*" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">8.31 </char>
      <char style="xq" closed="false">εἰ ὁ θεὸς ὑπὲρ ἡμῶν </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="PSA 118:6">Ps 118.6</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Τί οὖν ἐροῦμεν πρὸς ταῦτα; εἰ ὁ θεὸς ὑπὲρ ἡμῶν, τίς καθ᾽ ἡμῶν; <verse number="32" style="v" /><note caller="*" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">8.32 </char><char style="xq" closed="false">ὅς … παρέδωκεν αὐτόν </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JHN 3:16">Jn 3.16</ref></char></note>ὅς γε τοῦ ἰδίου υἱοῦ οὐκ ἐφείσατο ἀλλ᾽ ὑπὲρ ἡμῶν πάντων παρέδωκεν αὐτόν, πῶς οὐχὶ καὶ σὺν αὐτῷ τὰ πάντα ἡμῖν χαρίσεται; <verse number="33" style="v" /><note caller="*" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">8.33 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ISA 50:8">Is 50.8</ref></char></note>τίς ἐγκαλέσει κατὰ ἐκλεκτῶν θεοῦ; θεὸς ὁ δικαιῶν·<note caller="e" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">8.33 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Question: M NBS<char style="add">mg</char> TOB<char style="add">mg</char></char></note> <verse number="34" style="v" /><note caller="*" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">8.34 </char><char style="xq" closed="false">ὃς … δεξιᾷ τοῦ θεοῦ </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="PSA 110:1">Ps 110.1</ref> </char><char style="xq" closed="false">ὃς καὶ ἐντυγχάνει ὑπὲρ ἡμῶν </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="1JN 2:1">1 Jn 2.1</ref></char></note>τίς ὁ κατακρινῶν; Χριστὸς [Ἰησοῦς]<note caller="10" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">8.34 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">{C} </char><char style="fk" closed="false">Χριστὸς Ἰησοῦς </char><char style="ft" closed="false">ℵ A C F G L Ψ 6 33 81 104 256 365 424<char style="add">c</char> 436 1319 1573 1852 1962 2127 it<char style="add">b, f, g</char> vg syr<char style="add">h</char> cop<char style="add">bo</char> arm eth geo<char style="add">2</char> (geo<char style="add">1</char>) Origen<char style="add">lat</char> Didymus<char style="add">dub</char> Cyril; Pelagius Augustine<char style="add">3/4</char> Ps-Vigilius ⫽ </char><char style="fk" closed="false">ἅμα δὲ Χριστὸς Ἰησοῦς </char><char style="ft" closed="false">𝔓<char style="add">46vid</