  <chapter number="15" style="c" />
  <para style="s">Please Your Fellow Men, Not Yourself</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" />Ὀφείλομεν δὲ ἡμεῖς οἱ δυνατοὶ τὰ ἀσθενήματα τῶν ἀδυνάτων βαστάζειν καὶ μὴ ἑαυτοῖς ἀρέσκειν. <verse number="2" style="v" /><note caller="*" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">15.2 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ROM 14:19">Ro 14.19</ref>; <ref loc="1CO 9:19">1 Cor 9.19</ref>; <ref loc="1CO 10:24">10.24</ref>, <ref loc="1CO 10:33">33</ref></char></note>ἕκαστος ἡμῶν τῷ πλησίον ἀρεσκέτω εἰς τὸ ἀγαθὸν πρὸς οἰκοδομήν· <verse number="3" style="v" /><note caller="*" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">15.3 </char><char style="xq" closed="false">Οἱ … ἐμέ </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="PSA 69:9">Ps 69.9</ref></char></note>καὶ γὰρ ὁ Χριστὸς οὐχ ἑαυτῷ ἤρεσεν, ἀλλὰ καθὼς γέγραπται, <char style="qt">Οἱ ὀνειδισμοὶ τῶν ὀνειδιζόντων σε ἐπέπεσαν ἐπ᾽ ἐμέ.</char> <verse number="4" style="v" /><note caller="*" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">15.4 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ROM 4:23-24">Ro 4.23‑24</ref>; <ref loc="1CO 10:11">1 Cor 10.11</ref></char></note>ὅσα γὰρ προεγράφη, εἰς τὴν ἡμετέραν διδασκαλίαν ἐγράφη, ἵνα διὰ τῆς ὑπομονῆς καὶ διὰ τῆς παρακλήσεως τῶν γραφῶν τὴν ἐλπίδα ἔχωμεν. <verse number="5" style="v" />ὁ δὲ θεὸς τῆς ὑπομονῆς καὶ τῆς παρακλήσεως δῴη ὑμῖν τὸ αὐτὸ φρονεῖν ἐν ἀλλήλοις κατὰ Χριστὸν Ἰησοῦν, <verse number="6" style="v" />ἵνα ὁμοθυμαδὸν ἐν ἑνὶ στόματι δοξάζητε τὸν θεὸν καὶ πατέρα τοῦ κυρίου ἡμῶν Ἰησοῦ Χριστοῦ.</para>
  <para style="s">The Gospel for Jews and Gentiles Alike</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="7" style="v" />
    <note caller="*" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">15.7 </char>
      <char style="xq" closed="false">προσλαμβάνεσθε ἀλλήλους </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ROM 14:1">Ro 14.1</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Διὸ προσλαμβάνεσθε ἀλλήλους, καθὼς καὶ ὁ Χριστὸς προσελάβετο ὑμᾶς<note caller="1" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">15.7 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">{A} </char><char style="fk" closed="false">ὑμᾶς </char><char style="ft" closed="false">ℵ A C D<char style="add">2</char> F G Ψ 6 33 81 256 263 365 424 436 1175 1241 1319 1573 1739 1881 1912 1962 2127* 2200 <char style="it">Byz</char> [L] <char style="it">Lect</char> it<char style="add">d<char style="add">2</char>, f, g, gue</char> vg syr<char style="add">p, h</char> cop<char style="add">bo</char> arm eth geo slav Origen<char style="add">lat</char> Chrysostom Cyril; Ambrosiaster Pelagius Speculum ⫽ </char><char style="fk" closed="false">ἡμᾶς </char><char style="ft" closed="false">B D* P 048 0150 104 459 1506 1852 2127<char style="add">c</char> <char style="it">l</char> 147 <char style="it">l</char> 590 <char style="it">l</char> 597 <char style="it">l</char> 751 <char style="it">l</char> 884 <char style="it">l</char> 1159 <char style="it">l</char> 1441 it<char style="add">ar, b, d*, r, o</char> vg<char style="add">ms</char> cop<char style="add">sa</char> Theodoret<char style="add">lem</char> REB EU</char></note><note caller="a" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">15.7 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">C: WH GNB NIV NRSV REB EU NBS TOB DHH</char></note> εἰς δόξαν τοῦ θεοῦ. <verse number="8" style="v" /><note caller="*" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">15.8 </char><char style="xq" closed="false">Χριστὸν … θεοῦ </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="MAT 15:24">Mt 15.24</ref> </char><char style="xq" closed="false">τὰς ἐπαγγελίας τῶν πατέρων </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="MIC 7:20">Mic 7.20</ref>; <ref loc="ACT 3:25">Ac 3.25</ref></char></note>λέγω γὰρ Χριστὸν διάκονον γεγενῆσθαι περιτομῆς ὑπὲρ ἀληθείας θεοῦ, εἰς τὸ βεβαιῶσαι τὰς ἐπαγγελίας τῶν πατέρων, <verse number="9" style="v" /><note caller="*" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">15.9 </char><char style="xq" closed="false">τὰ δὲ … θεόν </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ROM 11:30">Ro 11.30</ref> </char><char style="xq" closed="false">Διὰ … ψαλῶ </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="PSA 18:49">Ps 18.49</ref> (<ref loc="2SA 22:50">2 Sm 22.50</ref>)</char></note>τὰ δὲ ἔθνη ὑπὲρ ἐλέους δοξάσαι τὸν θεόν, καθὼς γέγραπται,</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <char style="qt">Διὰ τοῦτο ἐξομολογήσομαί σοι ἐν ἔθνεσιν</char></para>
  <para style="q2">
    <char style="qt">καὶ τῷ ὀνόματί σου ψαλῶ.</char></para>
  <para style="m">
    <verse number="10" style="v" />
    <note caller="*" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">15.10 </char>
      <char style="xq" closed="false">Εὐφράνθητε … αὐτοῦ </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="DEU 32:43">Dt 32.43</ref>
      </char>
    </note>καὶ πάλιν λέγει,</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <char style="qt">Εὐφράνθητε, ἔθνη, μετὰ τοῦ λαοῦ αὐτοῦ.</char></para>
  <para style="m">
    <verse number="11" style="v" />
    <note caller="*" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">15.11 </char>
      <char style="xq" closed="false">Αἰνεῖτε … λαοί </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="PSA 117:1">Ps 117.1</ref>
      </char>
    </note>καὶ πάλιν,</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <char style="qt">Αἰνεῖτε, πάντα τὰ ἔθνη, τὸν κύριον</char></para>
  <para style="q2">
    <char style="qt">καὶ ἐπαινεσάτωσαν αὐτὸν πάντες οἱ λαοί.</char></para>
  <para style="m">
    <verse number="12" style="v" />
    <note caller="*" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">15.12 </char>
      <char style="xq" closed="false">Ἔσται … ἐλπιοῦσιν </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ISA 11:10">Is 11.10</ref>; <ref loc="REV 5:5">Re 5.5</ref></char>
    </note>καὶ πάλιν Ἠσαΐας λέγει,</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <char style="qt">Ἔσται ἡ ῥίζα τοῦ Ἰεσσαὶ</char></para>
  <para style="q2">
    <char style="qt">καὶ ὁ ἀνιστάμενος ἄρχειν ἐθνῶν,</char></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <char style="qt">ἐπ᾽ αὐτῷ ἔθνη ἐλπιοῦσιν.</char></para>
  <para style="m">
    <verse number="13" style="v" />ὁ δὲ θεὸς τῆς ἐλπίδος πληρώσαι ὑμᾶς πάσης χαρᾶς καὶ εἰρήνης ἐν τῷ πιστεύειν, εἰς τὸ περισσεύειν ὑμᾶς ἐν τῇ ἐλπίδι ἐν δυνάμει πνεύματος ἁγίου.</para>
  <para style="s">Paul’s Missionary Commission</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="14" style="v" />Πέπεισμαι δέ, ἀδελφοί μου, καὶ αὐτὸς ἐγὼ περὶ ὑμῶν ὅτι καὶ αὐτοὶ μεστοί ἐστε ἀγαθωσύνης, πεπληρωμένοι πάσης [τῆς] γνώσεως, δυνάμενοι καὶ ἀλλήλους νουθετεῖν. <verse number="15" style="v" /><note caller="*" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">15.15 </char><char style="xq" closed="false">διὰ … θεοῦ </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ROM 1:5">Ro 1.5</ref>; <ref loc="ROM 12:3">12.3</ref></char></note>τολμηρότερον δὲ ἔγραψα ὑμῖν ἀπὸ μέρους<note caller="b" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">15.15 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">C: AD M WH BJ NBS<char style="add">mg</char> TOB NRSV (REB) GNB NIV </char><char style="fk" closed="false">||</char></note> ὡς ἐπαναμιμνῄσκων ὑμᾶς<note caller="c" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">15.15 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">C: AD TR WH</char></note> διὰ τὴν χάριν τὴν δοθεῖσάν μοι ὑπὸ τοῦ θεοῦ <verse number="16" style="v" /><note caller="*" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">15.16 </char><char style="xq" closed="false">εἰς … ἔθνη </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ROM 11:13">Ro 11.13</ref> </char><char style="xq" closed="false">γένηται … εὐπρόσδεκτος </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="PHP 2:17">Php 2.17</ref></char></note>εἰς τὸ εἶναί με λειτουργὸν Χριστοῦ Ἰησοῦ εἰς τὰ ἔθνη, ἱερουργοῦντα τὸ εὐαγγέλιον τοῦ θεοῦ, ἵνα γένηται ἡ προσφορὰ τῶν ἐθνῶν εὐπρόσδεκτος, ἡγιασμένη ἐν πνεύματι ἁγίῳ. <verse number="17" style="v" />ἔχω οὖν [τὴν] καύχησιν ἐν Χριστῷ Ἰησοῦ τὰ πρὸς τὸν θεόν· <verse number="18" style="v" /><note caller="*" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">15.18 </char><char style="xq" closed="false">οὐ γὰρ … ἐμοῦ </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="2CO 3:5">2 Cor 3.5</ref></char></note>οὐ γὰρ τολμήσω τι λαλεῖν ὧν οὐ κατειργάσατο Χριστὸς δι᾽ ἐμοῦ εἰς ὑπακοὴν ἐθνῶν, λόγῳ καὶ ἔργῳ, <verse number="19" style="v" />ἐν δυνάμει σημείων καὶ τεράτων, ἐν δυνάμει πνεύματος [θεοῦ]<note caller="2" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">15.19 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">{C} </char><char style="fk" closed="false">πνεύματος θεοῦ </char><char style="ft" closed="false">𝔓<char style="add">46</char> ℵ D<char style="add">1</char> Ψ 0150 6 424 436 1175 1241 1506 1912 <char style="it">Byz</char> [L P] <char style="it">Lect</char> (<char style="it">l</char> 422 </char><char style="fk" closed="false">πνεύματος θεοῦ δυνάμει ἁγίου</char><char style="ft" closed="false">) it<char style="add">b</char> syr<char style="add">p, h</char> geo<char style="add">2</char> slav Origen<char style="add">lat2/3</char> Didymus<char style="add">dub1/3</char> Chrysostom Cyril<char style="add">1/2</char> ⫽ </char><char style="fk" closed="false">πνεύματος </char><char style="ft" closed="false">B NIV TOB BTI ⫽ </char><char style="fk" closed="false">πνεύματος ἁγίου </char><char style="ft" closed="false">A D<char style="add">*, 2</char> F G 33 81 104 256 263 365 459 1319 1573 1739 1852 1881 1962 2127 2200 <char style="it">l</char> 593 it<char style="add">ar, d, f, g, mon, o</char> vg syr<char style="add">h<char style="add">mg</char>, pal</char> cop<char style="add">sa, bo</char> arm eth geo<char style="add">1</char> Origen<char style="add">lat1/3</char> Athanasius Ps-Athanasius Apollinaris Didymus<char style="add">dub2/3</char> Cyril<char style="add">1/2</char>; Ambrosiaster Pelagius Augustine Speculum Ps-Vigilius<char style="add">2/2</char> REB</char></note>· ὥστε με ἀπὸ Ἰερουσαλὴμ καὶ κύκλῳ μέχρι τοῦ Ἰλλυρικοῦ πεπληρωκέναι τὸ εὐαγγέλιον τοῦ Χριστοῦ, <verse number="20" style="v" /><note caller="*" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">15.20 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="2CO 10:15-16">2 Cor 10.15‑16</ref></char></note>οὕτως δὲ φιλοτιμούμενον εὐαγγελίζεσθαι οὐχ ὅπου ὠνομάσθη Χριστός, ἵνα μὴ ἐπ᾽ ἀλλότριον θεμέλιον οἰκοδομῶ, <verse number="21" style="v" /><note caller="*" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">15.21 </char><char style="xq" closed="false">ὄψονται … συνήσουσιν </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ISA 52:15">Is 52.15</ref></char></note>ἀλλὰ καθὼς γέγραπται,</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <char style="qt">Οἷς οὐκ ἀνηγγέλη περὶ αὐτοῦ ὄψονται,</char></para>
  <para style="q2">
    <char style="qt">καὶ οἳ οὐκ ἀκηκόασιν συνήσουσιν.</char></para>
  <para style="s">Paul’s Plan to Visit Rome</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="22" style="v" />
    <note caller="*" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">15.22 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ROM 1:10-13">Ro 1.10‑13</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Διὸ καὶ ἐνεκοπτόμην τὰ πολλὰ τοῦ ἐλθεῖν πρὸς ὑμᾶς· <verse number="23" style="v" />νυνὶ δὲ μηκέτι τόπον ἔχων ἐν τοῖς κλίμασιν τούτοις, ἐπιποθίαν δὲ ἔχων τοῦ ἐλθεῖν πρὸς ὑμᾶς ἀπὸ πολλῶν ἐτῶν, <verse number="24" style="v" /><note caller="*" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">15.24 </char><char style="xq" closed="false">ἐλπίζω … ἐμπλησθῶ </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="1CO 16:6">1 Cor 16.6</ref></char></note>ὡς ἂν πορεύωμαι εἰς τὴν Σπανίαν<note caller="3" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">15.24 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">{A} </char><char style="fk" closed="false">Σπανίαν </char><char style="ft" closed="false">𝔓<char style="add">46</char> ℵ* A B C D F G P Ψ 0150 81 1506 1739 1852 1881 1962 2200 it<char style="add">ar, (b), d, f, g, mon, o</char> vg syr<char style="add">p</char> cop<char style="add">sa, bo</char> arm eth geo<char style="add">1</char> Origen<char style="add">lat</char> Chrysostom; Ambrosiaster Jerome Pelagius ⫽ </char><char style="fk" closed="false">Σπανίαν, ἐλεύσομαι πρὸς ὑμᾶς </char><char style="ft" closed="false">ℵ<char style="add">2</char> 6 33 104 256 263 365 424 436 459 1175 1241 1319 1573 1912 2127 <char style="it">Byz</char> [L] <char style="it">Lect</char> (<char style="it">Lect</char><char style="add">pt</char> </char><char style="fk" closed="false">Ἱσπανίαν</char><char style="ft" closed="false">) syr<char style="add">h</char> geo<char style="add">2</char> slav</char></note>· ἐλπίζω γὰρ διαπορευόμενος θεάσασθαι ὑμᾶς καὶ ὑφ᾽ ὑμῶν προπεμφθῆναι ἐκεῖ ἐὰν ὑμῶν πρῶτον ἀπὸ μέρους ἐμπλησθῶ. <verse number="25" style="v" /><note caller="*" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">15.25 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ACT 19:21">Ac 19.21</ref>; <ref loc="ACT 20:22">20.22</ref></char></note>νυνὶ δὲ πορεύομαι εἰς Ἰερουσαλὴμ διακονῶν τοῖς ἁγίοις. <verse number="26" style="v" /><note caller="*" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">15.26 </char><char style="xq" closed="false">κοινωνίαν … Ἰερουσαλήμ </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="1CO 16:1">1 Cor 16.1</ref>; <ref loc="2CO 8:1">2 Cor 8.1</ref>; <ref loc="2CO 9:2">9.2</ref>, <ref loc="2CO 9:12">12</ref></char></note>εὐδόκησαν γὰρ Μακεδονία καὶ Ἀχαΐα κοινωνίαν τινὰ ποιήσασθαι εἰς τοὺς πτωχοὺς τῶν ἁγίων τῶν ἐν Ἰερουσαλήμ. <verse number="27" style="v" /><note caller="*" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">15.27 </char><char style="xq" closed="false">τοῖς πνευματικοῖς … ἔθνη </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ROM 9:4">Ro 9.4</ref> </char><char style="xq" closed="false">εἰ γὰρ … λειτουργῆσαι αὐτοῖς </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="1CO 9:11">1 Cor 9.11</ref></char></note>εὐδόκησαν γὰρ καὶ ὀφειλέται εἰσὶν αὐτῶν· εἰ γὰρ τοῖς πνευματικοῖς αὐτῶν ἐκοινώνησαν τὰ ἔθνη, ὀφείλουσιν καὶ ἐν τοῖς σαρκικοῖς λειτουργῆσαι αὐτοῖς. <verse number="28" style="v" />τοῦτο οὖν ἐπιτελέσας καὶ σφραγισάμενος αὐτοῖς τὸν καρπὸν τοῦτον, ἀπελεύσομαι δι᾽ ὑμῶν εἰς Σπανίαν· <verse number="29" style="v" />οἶδα δὲ ὅτι ἐρχόμενος πρὸς ὑμᾶς ἐν πληρώματι εὐλογίας Χριστοῦ<note caller="4" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">15.29 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">{A} </char><char style="fk" closed="false">Χριστοῦ </char><char style="ft" closed="false">𝔓<char style="add">46</char> ℵ* A B C D F G P 6 81 424<char style="add">c</char> 1739 1852 1881 2200 it<char style="add">ar, b, d, f, g, mon, o</char> vg<char style="add">ww, st</char> cop<char style="add">sa, bo</char> geo<char style="add">1</char> Clement Origen<char style="add">lat</char>; Ambrosiaster Pelagius ⫽ </char><char style="fk" closed="false">τοῦ εὐαγγελίου τοῦ Χριστοῦ </char><char style="ft" closed="false">ℵ<char style="add">2</char> Ψ (0150 1506 </char><char style="fk" closed="false">Χριστοῦ τοῦ εὐαγγελίου</char><char style="ft" closed="false">) 33 104 256 365 424* 436 459 1175 1241 1319 1573 1912 1962 2127 <char style="it">Byz</char> [L] <char style="it">Lect</char> vg<char style="add">cl</char> syr<char style="add">p, h</char> geo<char style="add">2</char> slav Chrysostom ⫽ <char style="it">omit</char> 263 arm</char></note> ἐλεύσομαι.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="30" style="v" />
    <note caller="*" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">15.30 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="2CO 1:11">2 Cor 1.11</ref>; <ref loc="PHP 1:27">Php 1.27</ref>; <ref loc="COL 4:3">Col 4.3</ref>; <ref loc="2TH 3:1">2 Th 3.1</ref></char>
    </note>Παρακαλῶ δὲ ὑμᾶς[, ἀδελφοί,] διὰ τοῦ κυρίου ἡμῶν Ἰησοῦ Χριστοῦ καὶ διὰ τῆς ἀγάπης τοῦ πνεύματος συναγωνίσασθαί μοι ἐν ταῖς προσευχαῖς ὑπὲρ ἐμοῦ πρὸς τὸν θεόν, <verse number="31" style="v" />ἵνα ῥυσθῶ ἀπὸ τῶν ἀπειθούντων ἐν τῇ Ἰουδαίᾳ καὶ ἡ διακονία<note caller="5" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">15.31 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">{A} </char><char style="fk" closed="false">διακονία </char><char style="ft" closed="false">𝔓<char style="add">46</char> ℵ A C D<char style="add">2</char> Ψ 0150 6 33 81 104 256 263 365 424 436 459 1175 1241 1319 1506 1573 1739 1852 1881 1912 1962 2127 2200 <char style="it">Byz</char> [L P] <char style="it">Lect</char> it<char style="add">d<char style="add">2</char>, f, g</char> vg<char style="add">mss</char> syr<char style="add">p, h</char> cop<char style="add">sa, bo</char> arm geo slav Origen<char style="add">lat</char> Chrysostom ⫽ </char><char style="fk" closed="false">δωροφορία </char><char style="ft" closed="false">B D* F G it<char style="add">ar, b, d*, mon, o</char> (vg) Ambrosiaster Pelagius</char></note> μου ἡ εἰς Ἰερουσαλὴμ εὐπρόσδεκτος τοῖς ἁγίοις γένηται, <verse number="32" style="v" />ἵνα ἐν χαρᾷ ἐλθὼν πρὸς ὑμᾶς διὰ θελήματος θεοῦ συναναπαύσωμαι ὑμῖν<note caller="6" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">15.32 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">{C} </char><char style="fk" closed="false">ἐν χαρᾷ ἐλθὼν πρὸς ὑμᾶς διὰ θελήματος θεοῦ συναναπαύσωμαι ὑμῖν </char><char style="ft" closed="false">𝔓<char style="add">118vid</char> A C 0150 6 (33 </char><char style="fk" closed="false">θεοῦ καί</char><char style="ft" closed="false">) 81 256 263 365 424<char style="add">c</char> (1319 2127 </char><char style="fk" closed="false">συναναπαύσομαι</char><char style="ft" closed="false">) 1506<char style="add">vid</char> 1573 1739 (1852 <char style="it">omit</char> </char><char style="fk" closed="false">ἐν χαρᾷ</char><char style="ft" closed="false">) 1881<char style="add">c</char> (1881* </char><char style="fk"